{"tid":94864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]粵漢變人肉炸彈 與女子同歸於盡","createTime":"2017-01-25T14:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:32:33.000Z","uid":32407,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf5337b155d2ff91b2e0a8f5af6037ff4a73fa3","tid":94864,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170125/56219584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170125%2F56219584&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=c973bc87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170125%2F56219584&h=1197b855\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170125/56219584</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東梅州五華縣發生爆炸案。事發於昨晚8時許，當地警方接報，指該縣水寨鎮發生一宗爆炸案，導致2人死亡。<br />\n經初步了解，28歲周姓男死者因與25歲楊姓女死者出現感情糾紛，周男身上綁上爆炸物到當地一汽車城引爆，造成2人當場死亡。現場未傷及無辜和造成其他財產損失。<br />\n在事發車行不遠處開餐廳的姓曾東主向《蘋果》說，死者楊女是該車行老闆的女兒，與周男是夫妻，兩人育有一女。案發時小孩亦在場，幸由家屬及時抱走，沒有受傷。他表示，由於女方家人反對交往，導致周楊兩人離婚，有指周男想將女兒接回老家過年受阻，與女家爆發爭吵。當地消息亦指，因周男不同意與女方分手，最終引發慘案。<br />\n目前警方正在對案件開展進一步調查。<br />\n《蘋果》記者/南方網<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f313914e4f13a92cd223f146567eabf2872aea4","tid":94864,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf37ba7750ec0f9d065f08e43239481a806775f5","tid":94864,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ad38b432caac5cd762829ceb392d40bdb7a221","tid":94864,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"留低個女做乜"},{"pid":"248cf6b103dd363e0a99f15068ee9d1c2834dbc5","tid":94864,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}